cloud command for fink
======================

fink: https://github.com/finklabs/fink

Features include:

-  deploy cloudformation templates

Running tests
-------------

Please make sure to have good test coverage for your plugin so we can
always make sure your plugin runs with the upcoming fink version.

Run tests like so:

.. code:: bash

    $ python -m pytest -vv --cov-report term-missing tests/test_*
